OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,FFigures show that the number of people
OL,7,Fneeding hospice care could rise by as
OL,8,Fmuch as 43% over the next 20 years.
OL,10,FChief Executive of St David's Hospice
OL,11,FCare, Emma Saysell MBE, explained that
OL,12,Frising costs and a lack of sustainable
OL,13,Ffunding has made its financial
OL,14,Fsituation tenuous.
OL,16,FShe said: "This is the worst time
OL,17,Ffinancially that I think we've ever
OL,18,Ffaced. The national minimum wage
OL,19,Fincrease has cost the hospice over
OL,20,F#100,000.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
