OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,F"Couple that with the increase in
OL,7,Fnational insurance, that was another
OL,8,F#180,000. So we had to find #310,000
OL,9,Fliterally to stand still."
OL,11,FSt David's cares for 1,500 each year
OL,12,Fin the community and its in-patient
OL,13,Funit.
OL,15,FShe added: "We're delivering a huge
OL,16,Famount of hospice care in the area
OL,17,Fthat we cover. We can't afford not to
OL,18,Fbe here."
