OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,FAs well as clinical services, like
OL,7,Fcommunity-based palliative nurses and
OL,8,Fan in-patient unit, St David's Hospice
OL,9,FCare runs a day hospice, where people
OL,10,Fliving with a life-limiting diagnosis
OL,11,Fcan come in once a week for a group
OL,12,Fsession.
OL,14,FShe continued: "This is where patients
OL,15,Fcan come and meet other people in a
OL,16,Fsimilar situation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
