OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,F"When you're facing a life limiting
OL,7,Fillness, you feel very isolated and
OL,8,Fthink perhaps you're the only one. And
OL,9,Fso people come here and they can talk
OL,10,Fto people in a similar situation."
OL,12,FClaire Thompson has been attending
OL,13,Fthese sessions since January.
OL,15,FShe said: "We're not ill here. We are
OL,16,Fjust normal. I love it here. I love
OL,17,Fthe camaraderie, I love the jokes.
