OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,F"When I was told my diagnosis and it
OL,7,Fwas terminal, I went through the
OL,8,Fstages of grieving; anger, self pity
OL,9,Fand coming here taught me the
OL,10,Facceptance.
OL,12,F"It's made me start to enjoy life
OL,13,Fagain, and live life again. And that's
OL,14,Fwhat I do, that's what I get from
OL,15,Fcoming here."
OL,17,FHowever, Ms Saysell explained that non-
OL,18,Fclinical services like the day hospice
OL,19,Fcould face cuts if funding challenges
OL,20,Fcontinue.
