OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,F"I would never want to cut any
OL,7,Fclinical services because I know the
OL,8,Fhuge difference it makes to patients
OL,9,Fand family but if the funding crisis
OL,10,Fcontinues we will have to make tough
OL,11,Fchoices," she added.
OL,13,FSt David's Hospice Care, along with
OL,14,Fthe wider hospice sector in Wales, is
OL,15,Fcalling on the Welsh Government to
OL,16,Fintroduce a sustainable funding model
OL,17,Ffor the long-term security of hospices
OL,18,Fin Wales.
