OL,3,CHospices 'in funding crisis' despite
OL,4,Crising demand
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said: "We have
OL,7,Fsignificantly increased investment in
OL,8,Fhospice services during this Senedd
OL,9,Fterm, providing an extra #5.2m a year
OL,10,Fand #9.5m in one-off, cost-of-living
OL,11,Fgrants to help hospices continue to
OL,12,Fprovide their vital services.
OL,14,F"Work is continuing to develop a new
OL,15,Fcommissioning approach for hospices
OL,16,Ffor Wales to create a more sustainable
OL,17,Ffinancial model for the longer term."
