OL,6,FBut hospice bosses like Ms Saysell are
OL,7,Fcalling for solutions now. She said:
OL,8,F"Our situation is becoming quite
OL,9,Furgent.
OL,11,F"We need to know how the funding from
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Government is going to be
OL,13,Fsustainable and continued over the
OL,14,Fnext five to ten years."
